'''大衛·繆爾''' ({{lang-en|'''David Muir'''}}，{{bd|1973年|11月8日}}) 是[[美國|美國]]的一位新聞記者和主播。自2014年開始，他出任[[ABC世界新聞|ABC世界新聞]]的主播。他曾是美國出境頻率最高的電視記者之一<ref>{{cite web|title=ABC’s David Muir Was The Most-Used Reporter On Broadcast News In 2012|url=http://www.mediaite.com/online/abcs-david-muir-was-the-most-used-reporter-on-broadcast-news-in-2012/|accessdate=February 1, 2014|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826032813/https://www.mediaite.com/online/abcs-david-muir-was-the-most-used-reporter-on-broadcast-news-in-2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=12 to Watch in TV News|url=http://www.tvweek.com/np51_22pger_LR.pdf|accessdate=February 1, 2014|newspaper=TV Week|date=December 17, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207020352/http://www.tvweek.com/np51_22pger_LR.pdf|archivedate=2013年12月7日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=David Muir -- Brokaw, Eat Your Heart Out!|url=http://www.tmz.com/2009/03/11/david-muir-brokaw-eat-your-heart-out/|accessdate=February 1, 2014|newspaper=TMZ|date=March 11, 2009|archive-date=2018-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006213810/http://www.tmz.com/2009/03/11/david-muir-brokaw-eat-your-heart-out/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，他被《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物雜誌]]》列入最性感男士名單<ref>{{cite web|last=Connor|first=Jackson|date=November 20, 2014|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/20/abc-news-people-sexiest-men-alive-list-strahan-tebow-muir_n_6187712.html|title=ABC News Dominates People Magazine's 'Sexiest Men Alive' List|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|accessdate=November 22, 2014|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|archive-date=2017-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422160650/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/11/20/abc-news-people-sexiest-men-alive-list-strahan-tebow-muir_n_6187712.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

